 Wargasm 与 Limp Bizkit 的 Fred Durst 合作制作“Bang Ya Head” https://www.nme.com/news/music/wargasm-team-up-with-limp-bizkits-fred-durst-on-bang-ya-head-3495352?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=wargasm-team-与跛行 bizkits 弗雷德德斯特在邦亚头上Anagricel DuranFri, 08 Sep 2023 20:15:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3495352 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="从左到右：银河系、弗莱德·德斯特、山姆·马特洛克。图片来源：杰西卡-罗丝·莉娜" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌向 Limp Bizkit 的《My Generation》致敬</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wargasm-team-up-with-limp-bizkits-fred-durst-on-bang-ya-head-3495352">Wargasm 后与 Limp Bizkit 的 Fred Durst 合作的《Bang Ya Head》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="从左到右：银河系、弗莱德·德斯特、山姆·马特洛克。图片来源：杰西卡-罗丝·莉娜" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wargasm-and-Fred-Durst-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/wargasm">Wargasm</a>发布了他们最新的单曲“Bang Ya Head”，其中包括<a href="/artists/limp-bizkit">Limp Bizkit</a>的主唱 Fred Durst。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wargasm-download-2022-interview-radar-nu-metal-explicit-debut-album-3247406">Wargasm – “我们喜欢得到所有新金属爸爸的认可”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 《Bang Ya Head》是伦敦摇滚二人组（由 Milkie Way 和 Sam Matlock 组成）即将推出的首张唱片《Venom》中分享的第二首单曲。这是他们的第一首单曲“Do It So Good”之后的歌曲。</p><p>在新闻稿中谈到这首歌时，马特洛克说：“当我在酒吧工作时，它总是让我发疯，我们的生活成本是多少，而我们赚的钱却是那么少。世界变得他妈的疯狂，一切都变得如此昂贵——我们他妈的怎么才能买到生命呢？这只是一个噩梦循环，直到你幸运为止。就像一遍又一遍地用头撞砖墙一样——你不断地用头撞，直到你他妈的脖子折断。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="𝐖𝐀𝐑𝐆𝐀𝐒𝐌 - “Bang Ya Head Feat. Fred Durst”（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JQjZ3fQF75Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说道：“我们把这种能量放在洛杉矶朋友家里的一把吉他上，然后在浴室里的某个地方装上麦克风，这样邻居就不会太生气，然后我们问唯一的 Fred Durst 是否愿意他加入了——现在我们有了这个怪物。我们等你听到这个消息已经等了太久了。”</p><p>此前，两人曾在 Limp Bizkit 的“Still Sucks”巡演欧洲站中担任开场支持。 《Bang Ya Head》向 Bizkit 的经典歌曲《My Generation》致敬，并警告道：“你在丛林朋克中！”</p><p> Wargasm 即将推出的首张唱片“Venom”将于 10 月 27 日发行。 <a href="https://satellite414.us19.list-manage.com/track/click?u=16aaa3e2e45848f1982c1bd2e&amp;id=22e715df09&amp;e=277a1050ba" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预订。</p><p>在接受<em><a href="https://www.kerrang.com/wargasm-announce-heavy-melodic-disgusting-honest-sexy-debut-album-venom" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kerrang</a>采访时，</em>乐队将这张专辑描述为“沉重、旋律优美、恶心、诚实、性感”，并补充道：“自我们成立以来，这支乐队所尝试的一切都被钉在铁砧上，锤打成型，扔到了墙，被打成更糟糕的形状，然后又回到铁砧上。”</p><p>这对组合将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">Corey Taylor</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/royal-blood">Royal Blood</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/babymetal">Babymetal</a>以及他们自己的头条演出一起上路。<a href="https://www.wargasm.online/tour-dates" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>获取门票并查看完整的日期列表。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CuxCEFFN3Rc/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C54